      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "let him be ignorant.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " In some copies it is, he shall not be known: in the day of judgment Christ shalt say unto him: Depart from me, I know you not. ",
        "children": []
